            <guid>https://molentum.me/gallery/2024/ivu/</guid>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;The dryads, Ivu amongst them, are caretakers of the forest
and some of the most powerful magical beings in the world,
wielding shapeshifting growth and destructive fire
to drive nature&#x27;s cycles of death and rebirth ever onward.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Extra sketches exploring different balances between
nature&#x2F;gardening aesthetics and a fancy sorcerer&#x27;s dress:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</description>
