&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;molentum.me&#x2F;gallery&#x2F;2024&#x2F;mermay-inks&#x2F;mermay01.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Ink drawing of a mermaid with a spiky crown on her head. She&#x27;s looking away from the viewer at some fish and some kind of stone obelisk in the distance.&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;molentum.me&#x2F;gallery&#x2F;2024&#x2F;mermay-inks&#x2F;mermay03.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Ink drawing of a horned merman holding a spear and looking at a school of fish in the background.&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;molentum.me&#x2F;gallery&#x2F;2024&#x2F;mermay-inks&#x2F;mermay04.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Ink drawing of a mermaid with octopus tentacles for a tail. She&#x27;s holding a dagger, and the arm holding it is covered in strange tendrils and eyes. The background is full of snake-like eyeballs.&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;molentum.me&#x2F;gallery&#x2F;2024&#x2F;mermay-inks&#x2F;mermay05.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Ink drawing of a mermaid wearing a lace nightgown, with her arms spread out to the sides and a smirk on her face. Behind her lots of rocks are rising upward.&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;molentum.me&#x2F;gallery&#x2F;2024&#x2F;mermay-inks&#x2F;mermay06.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Ink drawing of a merman sitting relaxedly at the bottom of a shallow pond. You can see the water surface in the background with lily pads floating on it.&quot; &#x2F;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
</description>
